{
  "stem": "12666.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I imagined that most probably there would be some translation work to be done.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And later on, I found out that there were about 20,000 Americans working at Nuremberg, so there were quite a few Americans in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Mother was quite happy that I go to Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She says, justice has to be done, because war criminals have not been prosecuted after World War I, so something has to be done.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The idea of Nuremberg was-- just like President Wilson used to say that World War I is to stop all other wars, we were hoping that war crimes would stop after Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were hoping that this would be realized.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But now I'm awfully disappointed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "War crimes are being committed right and left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't learn any lesson from-- from Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was put right away into a hotel that was still being repaired, right next to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was well taken care of.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Later on I got some quarters in a nearby village, to be with other young Americans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- so it was very friendly, very friendly, very efficient.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had wonderful food, much better than it was in the Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] We had those fancy restaurants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Naturally, the dishes that they had, the silverware had a stamp of Reichsparteitag, Nuremberg, the city of the Party, or the Nazi Party.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, the first meal that I had there, all the forks and knives disappeared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody took a souvenir.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still have a fork with Reichsparteitag at home as a souvenir.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the lady next to me was [INAUDIBLE] says, take mine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You have a pocket.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Later on we were served, naturally, plastic dishes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Silver, the silverware was going as souvenir.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
